{{flavour|A small, stout humanoid said to be good at finding its way through underground passages. Once commonly found in dungeons across the world, gnomes are now on the verge of extinction. This one may be the last of its kind.}}

==Useful Info==
'''Gnomes''' are weak monsters based off of the obsolete [[gnome|species]]. They only appear in a rare entry vault based off of obsolete player species.

==Tips & Tricks==
They might be able to hurt you a bit if they find good equipment, but since they generally only appear in an entry vault, the only way they could get equipment would be if you deliberately gave them some.
